OL,6,FA mother who smothered her baby to
OL,7,Fdeath during a mental health episode
OL,8,Fhas been given an indefinite hospital
OL,9,Forder.
OL,11,FHayley MacFarlane killed five-month-
OL,12,Fold daughter Evelyn after leaving a
OL,13,FChristmas party at the mental health
OL,14,Funit in Leeds where she was being
OL,15,Ftreated on 20 December last year.
OL,17,FAfter the incident in Woodhouse Moor
OL,18,FPark she called her husband, who was
OL,19,Fdriving over to see her, and told him
OL,20,Fto pull over.
