OL,6,FShe told him Evelyn was "gone" before
OL,7,Fcalling 999 and telling police she had
OL,8,Fkilled her daughter.
OL,10,FThe 39-year-old, of Carrington Street,
OL,11,FBarnsley, was initially charged with
OL,12,Fmurder, but later admitted the charge
OL,13,Fof infanticide.
OL,15,FSheffield Crown Court heard she was
OL,16,Fnormally "caring and empathetic" but
OL,17,Fhad been suffering from post natal
OL,18,Fdepression and postpartum psychosis.
OL,20,FWhat is postpartum psychosis?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
