OL,6,FAccording to the NHS, postpartum
OL,7,Fpsychosis is a serious mental health
OL,8,Fillness that can affect someone soon
OL,9,Fafter having a baby.
OL,11,FAbout one in 1,000 mothers experiences
OL,12,Fthe condition.
OL,14,FSymptoms usually start suddenly within
OL,15,Fthe first two weeks and can include
OL,16,Fhallucinations, delusions, manic
OL,17,Fbehaviour, low mood, depression and
OL,18,Fconfusion.
