OL,6,FIt is unclear what causes postpartum
OL,7,Fpsychosis, but women are more at risk
OL,8,Fif they already have a diagnosis of
OL,9,Fbipolar disorder or schizophrenia.
OL,11,FUnlike the mild mood changes which
OL,12,Faffect many new mothers, it should be
OL,13,Ftreated as a medical emergency.
OL,15,FTreatment usually happens in hospital
OL,16,Fand can include medication,
OL,17,Felectroconvulsive therapy and
OL,18,Fpsychological therapy.
