OL,6,FAnyone at higher risk should be seen
OL,7,Fby a perinatal psychiatrist and have a
OL,8,Fpre-birth planning meeting at around
OL,9,F32 weeks of pregnancy with everyone
OL,10,Finvolved in their care.
OL,12,FThe court heard MacFarlane referred
OL,13,Fherself to a mental health team after
OL,14,FEvelyn's birth, having felt "dread"
OL,15,Fand guilt about her daughter.
OL,17,FShe was seen by a consultant but
OL,18,FEvelyn was feeding well and putting on
OL,19,Fweight.
