OL,6,FMacFarlane was given anti-depressants
OL,7,Fbut felt unable to take them. A month
OL,8,Fbefore Evelyn's death, she placed her
OL,9,Fbaby in a sink full of water.
OL,11,FShe was diagnosed with post natal
OL,12,Fdepression and detained under the
OL,13,FMental Health Act and remained an
OL,14,Finpatient in hospital until the day of
OL,15,FEvelyn's death.
