OL,6,FMacFarlane sobbed throughout the
OL,7,Fsentencing hearing. She was told by
OL,8,Fjudge Mrs Justice Lambert: "I am
OL,9,Fsatisfied that but for your condition
OL,10,Fof post-partum psychosis and your
OL,11,Fdepression, you would not have harmed
OL,12,Fyour baby."
